---
// Company Story — About § 2
---

<section id="story" class="py-24 bg-stone-100 dark:bg-background-dark/60">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start">

      <!-- Left: Story text -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="h-px w-12 bg-primary" />
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary font-display">Our Story</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-black uppercase text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 leading-tight" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">
            Architecture &amp;<br />Interior Design<br />Redefined
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 font-sans text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Design Sense is an architecture and interior design firm founded by Architect Anchal Garg. We have successfully delivered <strong class="text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-200">150+ projects pan India</strong> in the last 5 years across various typologies — residential bungalows, farmhouses, luxury apartments, commercial spaces, and educational institutions.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today we have a strong team of in-house design experts and associated consultants that help us provide our clients top-notch quality design service. Every project is approached with the same conviction: <em class="text-primary font-medium">saving the client's money, time &amp; stress.</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            We believe that great design is not a luxury — it is the result of listening carefully, planning meticulously, and executing flawlessly. Our photorealistic 3D visualization service ensures you see every detail of your space before construction begins.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-primary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-contrast px-7 py-3 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Explore Our Services
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Stat callout -->
      <div class="space-y-6 lg:pt-16">
        {[
          { num: '150+', label: 'Projects Delivered', desc: 'Residential · Commercial · Farmhouse · Apartments' },
          { num: '5+', label: 'Years of Practice', desc: 'Consistent quality and innovation since founding' },
          { num: 'Pan India', label: 'Project Footprint', desc: 'From Delhi NCR to Rewari and across cities' },
        ].map(({ num, label, desc }) => (
          <div
            class="p-6 rounded-lg border group hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors duration-300"
            style="border-color: var(--color-accent); border-color: #e7e0d8; background-color: var(--color-background-light);"
          >
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
              <span class="font-display font-black text-5xl text-primary leading-none">{num}</span>
              <span class="font-display font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">{label}</span>
            </div>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mt-2">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>